IMAPAccount personal
Host imap.gmail.com
User sumner.evans98@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass Mail/Offlineimap-Personal"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPAccount tef
Host imap.gmail.com
User sumner@the-evans.family
PassCmd "pass Mail/Offlineimap-tef"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPAccount mines
Host imap.gmail.com
User jonathanevans@mymail.mines.edu
PassCmd "pass Mail/Offlineimap-Mines"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

IMAPStore tef-remote
Account tef

IMAPStore mines-remote
Account mines

MaildirStore personal-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Personal/  # The trailing "/" is important
Inbox ~/Mail/Personal/INBOX

MaildirStore tef-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/TEF/  # The trailing "/" is important
Inbox ~/Mail/TEF/INBOX

MaildirStore mines-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/Mines/  # The trailing "/" is important
Inbox ~/Mail/Mines/INBOX

Channel personal-all
Master :personal-remote:
Slave :personal-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-inbox
Master :personal-remote:
Slave :personal-local:
Patterns INBOX
Create Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

Channel tef-all
Master :tef-remote:
Slave :tef-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

Channel tef-inbox
Master :tef-remote:
Slave :tef-local:
Patterns INBOX
Create Both
Remove Both
SyncState *

Channel mines-all
Master :mines-remote:
Slave :mines-local:
Pattern *
Create Both
Remove Both
